
<div id="signInModal" class="reveal-modal">
  <div class="fader"></div>
  <div>
  <div class="row pagination-centered">
    <div class="twelve columns">
      <h2>Here's, sign up!</h2>
      <h3>Don't be afraid, it's free!</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="seven columns sign-in-description">
      <p>After you have signed up, you can start keeping a history of films you have watched, the ones you love, even the ones you own! </p>
      <p>And creating your own film lists is a great way to recommend films to friends, and discover new ones yourself!</p> 
    </div>
    <div class="five columns sign-in-links">
      <a href="/auth/facebook" class="radius button" data-no-pjax id="authFacebook">
         <i class="icon-facebook"></i><strong>facebook</strong>
      </a> 
      <a class="radius button alert" href="/auth/netflix" data-no-pjax id="authNetflix">
        <%= image_tag '/assets/netflix-n-logo.png' %>
        <strong>Netflix</strong>
      </a>
      <a class="radius button" href="/auth/twitter" id="authTwitter">
        <i class="icon-twitter"></i><strong>twitter</strong>
      </a> 
      <a class="radius button success" href="/auth/google_oauth2" data-no-pjax id="authGoogle">
         <i class="icon-google-plus"></i><strong>Google</strong>
      </a> 
<!--       <a class="radius button" href="/auth/vimeo" data-no-pjax>
        <strong>Sign in with Vimeo</strong>
      </a>  -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row pagination-centered">
     <div class="twelve columns">
      <strong>None of the above?</strong>
      <br />
      We are adding more ways to get involved - so check again soon!
      <!-- <a href="/users/sign_up">Sign up with your email address</a> -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="close-reveal-modal">Ã—</a>
</div>
</div>